  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A continental buffet breakfast is available each morning. You can speak with the hotel on arrival about a hot breakfast (payable locally).</p>
<p>The restaurant has recently been done up and has a great atmosphere for dinner. Your evening meal is a choice of three courses and there's an extensive a la carte wine list with wines recommended by a sommelier, so you can try out some local and international labels.</p>
<p>There's also a weekly traditional gala dinner where you'll get to try local specialities.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
