  <description><![CDATA[<p>The small and cosy Hotel Sud Ovest is located at the top of the <a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea}" title="Sestriere">village, </a>close to the main shopping area. Run by the welcoming Roux family, you'll feel right at home here. </p>
<h2>Family run</h2>
<p>The cosy Hotel Sud Ovest is an excellent choice if you are looking for a simplistic hotel in a fantastic ski area. The ski lifts which take you up to the sunny slopes on the <a data-udi="umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c}" title="Milky Way Ski Area">Milky Way</a> are around 800 metres away, the local bus stop is very close so you can hop on and not worry about walking too far in ski boots. The experienced Roux family and their team are incredibly welcoming, be sure to ask them about their favourite ski runs - you might find a new favourite. </p>
<h2>Alpine cuisine </h2>
<p>Each morning start your day at the rich continental breakfast buffet including local cured meats, cheeses, homemade sweet treats, fresh fruit and dairy products. Each afternoon you can enjoy complimentary tea and biscuits to keep you going until dinner. There's a great atmosphere for dinner in the cosy restaurant, you can enjoy a choice of three courses from a menu inspired by traditional alpine cuisine. There's an extensive a la carte wine list with wines recommended by a sommelier, so you can try out some local and international labels. Stop by the bar for a digestif before heading to bed.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Sud Ovest the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
