  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sud Ovest is a small, family-run hotel in a good location. It's at the top of the village, close to the town centre. The lifts are 450 metres away and you can jump on the local bus that stops nearby. After skiing, head back for free afternoon tea and biscuits.</p>]]></listingDescription>
